title: ThirdParty 폴더 안에 아래의 3개 라이브러리를 빌드한다
완료된 이후 폴더 구조는 다음과 같다
미리 빌드한 Pangolin, OpenCV, Eigen3를 불러오기 위해 CMakeLists.txt를 수정한다

# find_package(OpenCV 4.4)
find_package(OpenCV 4.4 EXACT PATHS Thirdparty/OpenCV/install/lib/cmake/opencv4)

# find_package(Eigen3 3.1.0 REQUIRED)
# find_package(Pangolin REQUIRED)
find_package(Eigen3 3.3.4 EXACT REQUIRED PATHS Thirdparty/Eigen3/install/share/eigen3/cmake)
message("Eigen3: ${Eigen3_DIR}")
find_package(Pangolin REQUIRED HINTS Thirdparty/Pangolin/install/lib/cmake/Pangolin)
message("Pangolin: ${Pangolin_DIR}")
ASL Dataset Format 파일의 링크 주소를 복사한다
폴더를 생성한 뒤, 해당 폴더에 압축을 해제한다

title:
mkdir Pangolin && cd Pangolin
git clone --recursive https://github.com/stevenlovegrove/Pangolin.git
mkdir build/
mkdir install/

cd Pangolin
./scripts/install_prerequisites.sh recommended # ubuntu
cd ..

cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=../install ../Pangolin
make -j"$(nproc)"
sudo make install

mkdir OpenCV && cd OpenCV
wget -O opencv.zip https://github.com/opencv/opencv/archive/4.4.0.zip
unzip opencv.zip && rm opencv.zip
mkdir build/
mkdir install/
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=../install ../opencv-4.4.0
make -j"$(nproc)"
sudo make install

mkdir Eigen3 && cd Eigen3
git clone https://gitlab.com/libeigen/eigen.git
mkdir build/
mkdir install/
cd build
cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=../install ../eigen
make -j"$(nproc)"
sudo make install
